---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../../components/Footer.astro';
import OptimizedImage from '../../../components/OptimizedImage.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="TROVE - UX/UI | Portfolio ImStryker"
  description="Trove project page"
  lang="en"
>
  <Header lang="en" />
  
  <main class="bg-white dark:bg-[#121212]">
    
    <!-- HEADER SECTION -->
    <section class="hero-section text-center pt-32">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h1 class="title-main title-spacing">
          TROVE
        </h1>
        
        <!-- Role badges -->
        <div class="role-badges">
          <span>My role: UX/UI Designer</span>
          <span class="separator">|</span>
          <span>Web Designer</span>
          <span class="separator">|</span>
          <span>Front End Developer</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MOBILE SECTION (Video) -->
    <section class="video-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        <div class="video-container">
          <iframe
            src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/dxUyH-GCNa0?autoplay=1&mute=1&loop=1&playlist=dxUyH-GCNa0&controls=0&showinfo=0&rel=0&modestbranding=1&disablekb=1&iv_load_policy=3"
            title="Trove UX/UI Demo"
            frameborder="0"
            allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture"
            allowfullscreen
            class="video-iframe"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- STARTING POINT SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-spacing">
          STARTING<br>POINT
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Layout side by side: text left, statistics right -->
        <div class="side-by-side-layout">
          
          <!-- Left column: Problem description -->
          <div class="text-content">
            <p class="description-main description-spacing">
              Trove started as a beta without structure or clear strategy, which affected its conversion, retention and user acquisition
            </p>
            
            <!-- Secondary text -->
            <div class="secondary-text">
              <p>Onboarding was the biggest friction point: long and confusing, with an average time of 9 minutes and no visual guides. Additionally, lack of trust in service security generated 80% abandonment before completion.</p>
              
              <p>The product lacked a clear UX/UI structure, which affected understanding of its purpose: 75% of users had false expectations about its functionality and 7 out of 10 requested cancellation shortly after registering.</p>
              
              <p>It was necessary to rebuild the user experience from scratch, optimizing conversion, improving product perception and structuring the platform to make it more accessible and profitable.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Right column: Statistics grid -->
          <div class="stats-container">
            <!-- 2x2 statistics grid -->
            <div class="stats-grid-2x2">
              <!-- Stat 1 -->
              <div class="stat-item stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">9min</div>
                <div class="stat-description">Average time to complete onboarding</div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Stat 2 -->
              <div class="stat-item stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">80%</div>
                <div class="stat-description">Abandonment rate in onboarding</div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Stat 3 -->
              <div class="stat-item stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">75%</div>
                <div class="stat-description">False user expectation</div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Stat 4 -->
              <div class="stat-item stat-card">
                <div class="stat-number">7/10</div>
                <div class="stat-description">Early Cancellation Rate</div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- THE CHALLENGE SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-spacing">
          THE CHALLENGE
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Side by side layout: text left, image right -->
        <div class="side-by-side-layout">
          
          <!-- Left column: Challenge description -->
          <div class="text-content">
            <p class="description-main description-spacing">
              Transform Trove into a clear, trustworthy and scalable product, eliminating friction in the user experience that affected conversion, retention and service perception.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Secondary text -->
            <div class="secondary-text">
              <p>The biggest challenge was rebuilding the user experience from the ground up, eliminating friction that affected both product conversion and retention.</p>
              
              <p><strong>Clear objectives and components:</strong> The data and registration rate, eliminating friction that affected without reinforcing the perception of protection.</p>
              
              <p><strong>Product confusion:</strong> Many users saw it as a credit card, when it was actually an internal credit system based on subscription.</p>
              
              <p><strong>Low retention:</strong> No clear incentives for users to continue after their first year.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Right column: Product image -->
          <div class="image-container">
            <div class="project-image-large">
              <OptimizedImage 
                src="/images/projects/trove/trove-product-overview.jpg" 
                alt="Trove Product Overview"
                class=""
                loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
              />
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- REBUILD MOMENT SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section quote-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        <div class="quote-container">
          <h2 class="quote-title">
            IT WAS TIME TO REBUILD<br>
            THE EXPERIENCE AND CONVERT<br>
            TROVE INTO A SOLID<br>
            AND SCALABLE PRODUCT
          </h2>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ACTION PLAN SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-spacing">
          ACTION<br>PLAN
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Main description -->
        <p class="description-main description-spacing">
          Trove's restructuring was based on four pillars: improve onboarding to increase conversion, redesign the marketing site to educate users, optimize the webapp to strengthen retention and establish an SEO strategy to acquire customers organically.
        </p>
        
        <!-- 4 pillars grid -->
        <div class="pillars-grid">
          
          <!-- Pillar 1 -->
          <div class="pillar-item">
            <div class="pillar-number">01</div>
            <h3 class="pillar-title">Onboarding Optimization</h3>
            <p class="pillar-description">Onboarding was one of the main barriers for users, with a completion time of 9 minutes and an 80% abandonment rate. To improve conversion, I restructured the flow, reduced the number of steps and added visual indicators that guided the user through the process.</p>
            <div class="pillar-process">
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">UX</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Optimized user flow mapping</li>
                  <li>Implementation of visual feedback to reinforce trust</li>
                  <li>Creation of microinteractions to improve the feeling of progression</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">UI</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Form redesign to improve accessibility</li>
                  <li>Incorporation of a dynamic validation system</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">Front End</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Implementation of new flows in HTML, CSS and JavaScript</li>
                  <li>Onboarding load time optimization</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Pillar 2 -->
          <div class="pillar-item">
            <div class="pillar-number">02</div>
            <h3 class="pillar-title">Webapp Redesign</h3>
            <p class="pillar-description">The dashboard and internal interface failed to show the product's value, affecting user perception and retention. I redesigned the webapp to make it more intuitive, improving key information presentation and adding visual elements that reinforced the service's utility.</p>
            <div class="pillar-process">
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">UX</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Creation of a more intuitive navigation system</li>
                  <li>Dashboard design with clear and easy-to-interpret information</li>
                  <li>Implementation of subscription management improvements to avoid cancellations</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">UI</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Modern and accessible interface design, aligned with Trove's visual identity</li>
                  <li>Incorporation of interactive graphics to visualize user evolution</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">Front End</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Frontend development with HTML, CSS, JavaScript and PHP</li>
                  <li>Mobile device experience optimization</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Pillar 3 -->
          <div class="pillar-item">
            <div class="pillar-number">03</div>
            <h3 class="pillar-title">Marketing Site Redesign</h3>
            <p class="pillar-description">Many users confused the product with a traditional credit card and abandoned the process by not understanding how it worked. To solve this, I worked on a clear content strategy and a more intuitive design to properly convey the value proposition.</p>
            <div class="pillar-process">
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">UX</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Information architecture simplification</li>
                  <li>Creation of explanatory sections with conversion-oriented copywriting</li>
                  <li>Inclusion of visual elements that reinforce trust (testimonials, FAQs, certifications)</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">UI</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Complete site redesign with clearer visual hierarchy</li>
                  <li>Improved presentation of benefits and product functionality</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">Front End</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>WordPress implementation with Elementor, using HTML, CSS and PHP for better customization</li>
                  <li>Creation of specific landings for acquisition campaigns</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Pillar 4 -->
          <div class="pillar-item">
            <div class="pillar-number">04</div>
            <h3 class="pillar-title">SEO Project Creation</h3>
            <p class="pillar-description">User acquisition cost only became profitable after the second month of subscription, making capture through Ads unsustainable. I designed an SEO strategy focused on attracting customers organically and reducing dependence on paid advertising.</p>
            <div class="pillar-process">
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">SEO</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Keyword analysis and strategic content definition</li>
                  <li>Technical site optimization to improve Google indexing</li>
                  <li>Blog implementation with articles aimed at attracting relevant traffic</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">UX/UI</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>Creation of content structures optimized for SEO</li>
                  <li>Landing page design focused on organic conversion</li>
                  <li>Website component design</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <div class="process-category">
                <h4 class="process-category-title">Implementation</h4>
                <ul class="process-category-list">
                  <li>WordPress implementation with Elementor, using HTML and CSS for better customization</li>
                  <li>System to import company data using Google Sheets, WP import, ACF and Elementor</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ONBOARDING OPTIMIZATION SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-spacing">
          Onboarding Optimization
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Side by side layout: text left, results right -->
        <div class="side-by-side-layout">
          
          <!-- Left column: Process description -->
          <div class="text-content">
            <p class="description-main description-spacing">
              The first was a user pathway through a 9-minute completion time and 80% abandonment rate. To improve conversion, I restructured the flow, reduced information and integrated a trust experience.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Detailed process -->
            <div class="secondary-text process-list">
              <p><strong>UX</strong></p>
              <p>• Optimized user flow registration to reduce confusion.</p>
              <p>• Simple and intuitive user experience improvement.</p>
              <p>• Significantly improved conversion.</p>
              
              <p><strong>UI</strong></p>
              <p>• Form reduction to improve trust.</p>
              <p>• Dynamic validation system integration.</p>
              
              <p><strong>Front End</strong></p>
              <p>• Implementation of new flows in HTML, CSS and JavaScript.</p>
              <p>• Onboarding load time optimization.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Right column: Results -->
          <div class="results-container">
            <div class="results-grid">
              
              <!-- Result 1 -->
              <div class="result-item">
                <div class="result-before">
                  <span class="result-label">Before</span>
                  <span class="result-number">9min</span>
                  <span class="result-description">Average time to complete onboarding</span>
                </div>
                <div class="result-arrow">→</div>
                <div class="result-after">
                  <span class="result-label">After</span>
                  <span class="result-number">4min</span>
                  <span class="result-description">55% time reduction</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Result 2 -->
              <div class="result-item">
                <div class="result-before">
                  <span class="result-label">Before</span>
                  <span class="result-number">20%</span>
                  <span class="result-description">Conversion</span>
                </div>
                <div class="result-arrow">→</div>
                <div class="result-after">
                  <span class="result-label">After</span>
                  <span class="result-number">60%</span>
                  <span class="result-description">200% conversion improvement</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
        
        <!-- Onboarding mockups -->
        <div class="mockups-section">
          <div class="mockups-grid">
            
            <!-- Mockup 1 -->
            <div class="mockup-item">
              <div class="mockup-image">
                <OptimizedImage 
                  src="/images/projects/trove/onboarding-before.jpg" 
                  alt="Onboarding Before"
                  class=""
                  loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                />
              </div>
              <div class="mockup-caption">
                <span class="mockup-label">Before</span>
                <span class="mockup-description">Long and confusing 9-minute process</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Mockup 2 -->
            <div class="mockup-item">
              <div class="mockup-image">
                <OptimizedImage 
                  src="/images/projects/trove/onboarding-after.jpg" 
                  alt="Onboarding After"
                  class=""
                  loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                />
              </div>
              <div class="mockup-caption">
                <span class="mockup-label">After</span>
                <span class="mockup-description">Optimized flow with visual guides</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- WEBAPP REDESIGN SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-spacing">
          Webapp Redesign
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Main description -->
        <p class="description-main description-spacing">
          The dashboard and internal interface failed to retain users, affecting value perception and attention. I redesigned the application making it more dynamic, improved data presentation and established intuitive navigation.
        </p>
        
        <!-- Detailed process -->
        <div class="process-section">
          <div class="process-grid">
            
            <!-- UX -->
            <div class="process-item">
              <h3 class="process-title">UX</h3>
              <ul class="process-list">
                <li>Redesigned more intuitive navigation system.</li>
                <li>Dashboard design with clear and quick-to-interpret information.</li>
                <li>Modern and accessible interface implementation.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- UI -->
            <div class="process-item">
              <h3 class="process-title">UI</h3>
              <ul class="process-list">
                <li>Modern and accessible interface design, elevated Trove's visual identity.</li>
                <li>Creation of system graphics for a more attractive experience.</li>
                <li>Frontend development with HTML, CSS, JavaScript and PHP.</li>
                <li>Onboarding load time optimization.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Webapp mockups -->
        <div class="webapp-mockups">
          <div class="webapp-grid">
            
            <!-- Mockup 1 -->
            <div class="webapp-item">
              <div class="webapp-image">
                <OptimizedImage 
                  src="/images/projects/trove/webapp-dashboard.jpg" 
                  alt="Webapp Dashboard"
                  class=""
                  loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Mockup 2 -->
            <div class="webapp-item">
              <div class="webapp-image">
                <OptimizedImage 
                  src="/images/projects/trove/webapp-mobile.jpg" 
                  alt="Webapp Mobile"
                  class=""
                  loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Mockup 3 -->
            <div class="webapp-item">
              <div class="webapp-image">
                <OptimizedImage 
                  src="/images/projects/trove/webapp-interface.jpg" 
                  alt="Webapp Interface"
                  class=""
                  loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- MARKETING SITE REDESIGN SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-spacing">
          Marketing Site Redesign
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Side by side layout: text left, mockups right -->
        <div class="side-by-side-layout">
          
          <!-- Left column: Description -->
          <div class="text-content">
            <p class="description-main description-spacing">
              Many users confused the product with a traditional credit card and abandoned before converting. This led to creating clear communication about the value proposition.
            </p>
            
            <!-- Detailed process -->
            <div class="secondary-text process-list">
              <p><strong>UX</strong></p>
              <p>• Information architecture optimization.</p>
              <p>• Creation of explanatory sections with conversion-oriented copywriting.</p>
              <p>• Inclusion of technological trust elements, FAQ, certifications.</p>
              
              <p><strong>UI</strong></p>
              <p>• Complete site redesign with clearer visual hierarchy.</p>
              <p>• Improved presentation of benefits and product functionality.</p>
              
              <p><strong>Front End</strong></p>
              <p>• Implementation of new flows in HTML, CSS and JavaScript.</p>
              <p>• WordPress element optimization for better demonstration.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Right column: Mockups -->
          <div class="marketing-mockups">
            <div class="marketing-grid">
              
              <!-- Desktop -->
              <div class="marketing-item">
                <div class="marketing-image">
                  <OptimizedImage 
                    src="/images/projects/trove/marketing-desktop.jpg" 
                    alt="Marketing Desktop"
                    class=""
                    loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <!-- Mobile -->
              <div class="marketing-item">
                <div class="marketing-image">
                  <OptimizedImage 
                    src="/images/projects/trove/marketing-mobile.jpg" 
                    alt="Marketing Mobile"
                    class=""
                    loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                  />
                </div>
              </div>
              
            </div>
          </div>
          
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- SEO PROJECT CREATION SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-spacing">
          SEO Project Creation
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Main description -->
        <p class="description-main description-spacing">
          User acquisition cost was very high due to expensive advertising. I developed an SEO strategy to reduce dependence on paid advertising and reduce CAC.
        </p>
        
        <!-- SEO results -->
        <div class="seo-results">
          <div class="seo-stats">
            
            <!-- Stat 1 -->
            <div class="seo-stat">
              <div class="seo-number">35%</div>
              <div class="seo-description">Organic users of total</div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Stat 2 -->
            <div class="seo-stat">
              <div class="seo-number">$18 → $8</div>
              <div class="seo-description">CAC reduction (56%)</div>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- SEO process -->
        <div class="seo-process">
          <div class="seo-grid">
            
            <!-- UX/UI -->
            <div class="seo-item">
              <h3 class="seo-title">UX/UI</h3>
              <ul class="seo-list">
                <li>Keyword analysis and strategic content definition.</li>
                <li>Technical site optimization to improve indexing and UX.</li>
                <li>Creation of landing pages with high organic conversion.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Implementation -->
            <div class="seo-item">
              <h3 class="seo-title">Implementation</h3>
              <ul class="seo-list">
                <li>WordPress development with Elementor, using HTML, CSS and PHP.</li>
                <li>Configuration of analytical and SEO tools for monitoring.</li>
                <li>Optimization of reusable components for scalability.</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- SEO mockups -->
        <div class="seo-mockups">
          <div class="seo-mockups-grid">
            
            <!-- Landing page -->
            <div class="seo-mockup">
              <div class="seo-image">
                <OptimizedImage 
                  src="/images/projects/trove/seo-landing.jpg" 
                  alt="SEO Landing Page"
                  class=""
                  loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- Mobile SEO -->
            <div class="seo-mockup">
              <div class="seo-image">
                <OptimizedImage 
                  src="/images/projects/trove/seo-mobile.jpg" 
                  alt="SEO Mobile"
                  class=""
                  loading="lazy"
                retries={3}
                />
              </div>
            </div>
            
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FINAL RESULTS SECTION -->
    <section class="content-section results-final-section">
      <div class="container mx-auto custom-padding" style="max-width: 1880px;">
        
        <!-- Main title -->
        <h2 class="section-title section-title-spacing">
          RESULTS
        </h2>
        
        <!-- Final results grid -->
        <div class="final-results-grid">
          
          <!-- Conversion -->
          <div class="final-result-item">
            <div class="final-result-category">Conversion</div>
            <div class="final-result-main">
              <span class="final-result-number">20% → 60%</span>
              <span class="final-result-improvement">+200%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="final-result-description">Onboarding conversion improvement</div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Time -->
          <div class="final-result-item">
            <div class="final-result-category">Efficiency</div>
            <div class="final-result-main">
              <span class="final-result-number">9min → 4min</span>
              <span class="final-result-improvement">-55%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="final-result-description">Registration time reduction</div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Retention -->
          <div class="final-result-item">
            <div class="final-result-category">Retention</div>
            <div class="final-result-main">
              <span class="final-result-number">Cancellations</span>
              <span class="final-result-improvement">-40%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="final-result-description">Early cancellation reduction</div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- CAC -->
          <div class="final-result-item">
            <div class="final-result-category">Acquisition</div>
            <div class="final-result-main">
              <span class="final-result-number">$18 → $8</span>
              <span class="final-result-improvement">-56%</span>
            </div>
            <div class="final-result-description">Acquisition cost reduction</div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Experience -->
          <div class="final-result-item">
            <div class="final-result-category">Experience</div>
            <div class="final-result-main">
              <span class="final-result-number">7.7/10</span>
